<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_116" id="56v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_116_r2l24">Vicʒtumen cʒu Amberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_116_r2l25"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her vicʒtum / Als Jr nehſt mit etlıchen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freund<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l27">vnd Ratgeſellen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_116_line_1574924016386_70">hie </ab></add> geredt habt / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_116_r2l26">als ſıe vns geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ vvir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> kauffleute </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l28">
<del rend="strikethrough">daran weẏſen wolle ſie mit vns reden wolten </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_116_line_1574924084627_83">daʒ </ab></add> ſıe von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l29"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen an vns bringen ſolten / daʒ vvir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> kauffleut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l30">daran weıſten / daʒ ſıe die ſtraſʒ für den <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>markt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l31">pawen wolten / vnd das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir alſo getan / vnd als nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l32">
<add><ab facs="#facs_116_r1l3">des <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tags </ab></add> etlich <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> kauffleut mit <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab vnd kauffmanſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l33"> <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſtraſʒ pawen wolten / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Do ſind hinauſʒ </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_116_line_1574924154065_94">vnd </ab></add> für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l34">fewht hinauſʒ <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> / Do komen des wygelaıs Schenken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l35">diener vnd <expan>trib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die mit gevvalt wider hinter ſich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l36">hinein gen feuht / vnd nötten die daʒ ſie Jn gelt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l37">cʒu geleẏte <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> muſten / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd al </del> Nu wiſʒt Jr wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l38">daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">man </del> vormals mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_116_line_1574924271480_116"><expan>gned<ex>igen</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> künıg auſʒgetrage<ex>n</ex></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_line_1574924277768_121">iſt worden / daʒ man <expan>kheine<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>rn</expan> cʒu <expan>dheıne<ex>m</ex></expan> geleyte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l41">nötten 
<del rend="strikethrough">no </del> oder dringen ſol 
<del rend="strikethrough"> t / Eʒ beger Er wöll eʒ <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_116_r2l42">Er beger ſein <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd wöll das <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_117" id="57r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_117_r2l1">daʒ Jr <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen mit dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> wẏgeleis <expan>Schenke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_117_r2l2">vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des künigs wegen <expan>auſʒtrage<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_117_r2l3">vnd beſtellen wöllet / daʒ man die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒu <expan>ſolche<ex>m</ex></expan> geleit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_117_r2l4">vngedrungen vnd vngenötet laſſe / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_117_r2l5"><expan>bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gütlıch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wıder cʒuvviſſen </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_116" id="56v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Vicztumen czu Amberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her vicztum, als ir nehst mit etlichen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>freund<ex>en</ex></expan> und ratgesellen <add>hie</add> geredt habt,
                            <add>als sie uns gesagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>,
                            <add>daz</add> sie von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen an uns bringen
                        solten, daz wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> kauffleut daran weisten, daz
                        sie die strasz für den <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>markt</expan> pawen wolten, und
                        das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir also getan; und als nu <add>des
                                    <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tags</add> etlich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> kauffleut mit
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab und kauffmanschaft
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> strasz pawen wolten <add>und</add>
                        für Fewht hinausz <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, do komen des Wygelais
                        Schenken diener und <expan>trib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die mit gewalt wider
                        hinter sich hinein gen Feuht und nötten die, daz sie in gelt czu geleyte
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> musten. Nu wiszt ir wol, daz vormals
                        mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<add><expan>gned<ex>igen</ex></expan></add>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> künig,
                            auszgetrage<ex>n</ex> ist worden, daz man
                            <expan>kheine<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>rn</expan> czu
                                <expan>dheine<ex>m</ex></expan> geleyte nötten oder dringen sol, er
                        beger sein <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>, und wöll das
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, <pb facs="#facs_117" id="57r"/>daz ir
                                <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen mit dem
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Wygeleis
                            <expan>Schenke<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des künigs, wegen
                            <expan>ausztrage<ex>n</ex></expan> und bestellen wöllet, daz man die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czu <expan>solche<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        geleit ungedrungen und ungenötet lasse. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc. Und <expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gütlich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider czuwissen.</ab>
</div>
